Adjusting the USB transmission speed can increase the frequency of USB sending, and the speed of keyboard and mouse message sending will increase. However, the actual response speed depends on the performance of your phone. If the performance of your phone is weak but the sending speed is fast, it may cause message blocking, resulting in a high frequencies are not as smooth as low frequencies. Therefore, after adjustment, it is necessary to testing in the game to find the best matching speed!

This function is used to optimize the gun jump issue after the first shot. While opening, the second bullet can maintain a horizontal position similar to the first bullet, greatly improving the hit rate of the first few shots!

This function can eliminate the gun forzen time of the game after the shot(scope off) stops, recover run state faster, reduce the probability of being hit, with better effect in first person mode!(Long press to set more parameters)

When the AI continues shoot is ON, the device will dynamically set whether to continues shoot and auto adjust the continues shoot speed. Ctrl+4 can adjust the continues shoot speed of the current gun, and it will be auto saved.

AI crosshair function will auto add crosshair while no scope or scope not open, will be easy to aim while no scope. You can set style for every gun and scope in AI result float window. Long press call the position adjust window.

In games, recoil force of guns may be uneven. Open the AI dynamic gun press to set the dynamic gun press force for each gun to match the uneven recoil force, makes the gun press more stable. Set it ON, there is an default preset dynamic setting, which can be used directly. You can also click the \"dynamic adjustment\" button in the game recognition window to adjust the dynamics for each gun! See the video for details

The ratio of AI gun pressure is used to adjust the final percentage of AI gun pressure, and the final gun pressure data will be multiplied by this percentage, making it convenient to make subtle adjustments when importing gun pressure data due to different mobile phones, without the need to adjust every gun. If you do not understand this parameter, please use 100%

Smart Volume is used to shortly increase the volume, for example, when the footsteps is very low in the room, open this may hear it. After turning on this switch, press ~+F5 to turn On/Off this function. It is recommended to turn it on when needed and turn it off normally to protect hearing!

The intelligent probe is used to assist in probe shooting, automatically turning off the probe when stopping shooting to avoid forgetting to turn off the probe or pressing the wrong left and right probes, which may cause slow retraction and result in being hit in the head and eliminated. It can minimize the area and duration of body exposure to the greatest extent possible, and in critical cases, it can save lives with 1 blood!

The smart first person function automatically uses first person firing during AI no scope shooting, and immediately switches back to third person after the firing stops. This function can expand the field of view, improve shooting accuracy, increase shooting angles that are not available in third person, and improve battle ability in the game! Usage: Add a key and place it on the first/third person. Modify its properties to Smart 1st/3rd person(AI).Long press to adjust its parameters!

This parameter modifies the vertical sensitivity of the perspective movement. Normally, you can use 100%, which is the same with the horizontal sensitivity. If you want the sensitivity of the horizontal and vertical to be different, you can modify this parameter!

Screen casting mode has 2 modes. 1st: some mobile phones must use this mode, such as some Lenovo tablets. 2nd: when the user wants to project the screen to the TV or monitor to solve the problem of the screen being too small. While cast screen to monitor, you need to open the \'cast screen to monitor\' and check the resolution of your monitor and fill in the bottom, otherwise the cast screen may not be correct. See the tutorial for details!
